00:11:02.620 --> 00:11:05.580
God said, let the waters bring forth abundantly

00:11:05.580 --> 00:11:07.380
the moving creature that hath life

00:11:07.380 --> 00:11:10.180
and fowl that they may fly above the earth

00:11:10.180 --> 00:11:12.340
in the open firmament of heaven.

00:11:12.340 --> 00:11:14.940
God created great whales and every living creature

00:11:14.940 --> 00:11:17.500
that moveth which the waters brought forth abundantly

00:11:17.500 --> 00:11:22.060
after their kind and every winged fowl after his kind.

00:11:22.060 --> 00:11:24.100
And God saw that it was good.

00:11:24.100 --> 00:11:26.540
And God blessed them saying, be fruitful and multiply

00:11:27.100 --> 00:11:28.060
and fill the waters in the seas

00:11:28.060 --> 00:11:30.340
and let fowl multiply in the earth.

00:11:30.340 --> 00:11:32.620
And the evening and the morning were the fifth day.

00:11:32.620 --> 00:11:34.660
And you understand, I'm going through this quickly.

00:11:34.660 --> 00:11:36.620
I'm not studying tonight creation,

00:11:36.620 --> 00:11:39.340
but the reality is that as we read this account,

00:11:39.340 --> 00:11:43.580
we're amazed at the might and the strength of our God.

00:11:43.580 --> 00:11:47.220
And as he reveals himself as this name Elohim

00:11:47.220 --> 00:11:50.860
and the connection of Elohim to creation.

00:11:50.860 --> 00:11:55.420
And he created, we've referenced already a couple of times

00:11:55.420 --> 00:11:59.380
after their kind with the ability to reproduce

00:11:59.380 --> 00:12:02.260
after their kind in order to sustain

00:12:02.260 --> 00:12:04.660
all that he intended to be sustained.

00:12:04.660 --> 00:12:06.060
It says in verse 24,

00:12:06.060 --> 00:12:08.620
and God so let the earth bring forth the living creature

00:12:08.620 --> 00:12:11.260
after his kind, cattle and creeping thing

00:12:11.260 --> 00:12:13.500
and the beast of the earth after his kind.

00:12:13.500 --> 00:12:16.980
