00:15:46.140 --> 00:15:49.300
John chapter number one in verse number three.

00:15:49.300 --> 00:15:52.540
Colossians chapter number one verses 16 and 17.

00:15:52.540 --> 00:15:57.540
Very plain that Jesus Christ is the one

00:15:58.060 --> 00:16:00.060
