00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:43.460
that are being communicated to us,

00:17:43.460 --> 00:17:46.820
that it impacts our lives.

00:17:46.820 --> 00:17:50.580
Because our God is the creator.

00:17:50.580 --> 00:17:54.740
Our God is the one that said let there be light

00:17:54.740 --> 00:17:55.860
